The paper proposes a row-parallel architecture for the real-time implementation of bivariate algebraic integer (AI) encoded 2-D discrete cosine transform (DCT) for image and video processing. This involves the use of algorithms and techniques related to digital signal processing (DSP), image and video processing, and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.ET (Embedded Systems).
